; Examples from Computer Science Logo Style, Volume 2, Chapter 10: Iteration, Templates, and Tools
; Source URL: https://people.eecs.berkeley.edu/~bh/v2ch10/iter.html

foreach [print (sentence [I like] ?)] [chocolate [rum raisin] pumpkin]
print apply [sum ? 3] [5]
print apply [word (first ?1) (first ?2)] [Peter Dickinson]
show map [product ? ?] [1 2 3 4]
show map [first ?] [every good boy does fine]

to swap :pair
output list last :pair first :pair
end

show map [swap ?] [[Sherlock Holmes] [James Pibble] [Nero Wolfe]]
print count [how now brown cow]

